headline: PSEG Declares Regular Quarterly Dividend for the Fourth Quarter of 2024
summary: The Board of Directors of Public Service Enterprise Group (NYSE:PEG) today declared a $0.60 per share dividend on the outstanding common stock of the company for the fourth quarter of 2024.
